<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a855f7, #ec4899); color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; }
        .card-box { background: white; border: 2px solid #a855f7; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; font-family: monospace; font-size: 16px; word-break: break-all; }
        .footer { text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 12px; padding: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>✦ 数字商店</h1>
            <p>您的订单已完成</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>尊敬的用户，您好！</p>
            <p>您的订单 <strong>#{{ order.id }}</strong> 已支付成功。以下是您购买的商品信息：</p>

            <h3>商品信息</h3>
            <p><strong>商品名称：</strong>{{ card.product.name }}</p>
            <p><strong>订单金额：</strong>¥{{ order.total_amount }}</p>

            <h3>卡密内容</h3>
            <div class="card-box">
                {{ card.content }}
            </div>

            <p><small>* 请妥善保管您的卡密信息</small></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 数字商店 · 感谢您的购买</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
